OL,3,CTeenager taken to hospital after a
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FA teenager has been taken to hospital
OL,7,Fafter a stabbing in Liverpool.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,10,Farea near the Royal Albert Dock at
OL,11,Faround 7.55pm on Tuesday 7 April,
OL,12,Fafter reports a 15-year-old boy had
OL,13,Fbeen assaulted close to the currently
OL,14,Fclosed Tate museum.
OL,16,FMerseyside Police said he suffered a
OL,17,Fpuncture wound to his arm and was
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
OL,20,FHis injuries are not believed to be
OL,21,Flife-threatening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
