OL,3,CTeenager taken to hospital after a
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FMultiple police vehicles and two
OL,7,Fambulances were also in attendance.
OL,9,FA staff member at Buco Turkish BBQ
OL,10,FStreet Food said the incident appeared
OL,11,Fto take place shortly before 8pm.
OL,13,FHe said: "It happened at about 8pm. I
OL,14,Fthink it was a fight between a group
OL,15,Fof boys. One of them, aged around 16,
OL,16,Fcame to my truck. His arm was covered
OL,17,Fin blood.
OL,19,F"I gave him some water. I don't know
OL,20,Fif he was stabbed or if it was just a
OL,21,Fserious fight."
