OL,3,CTeenager taken to hospital after a
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FAn investigation is ongoing, with
OL,7,Fofficers carrying out witness
OL,8,Fenquiries and reviewing CCTV footage
OL,9,Fin the area.
OL,11,FChief Inspector Chris Bland said:
OL,12,F"Enquiries are in the early stages as
OL,13,Fwe seek to establish what has taken
OL,14,Fplace.
OL,16,F"We would ask anyone who was at the
OL,17,FAlbert Dock this evening who heard or
OL,18,Fsaw anything or has any information to
OL,19,Fcontact us."
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOU{D@LO]
